DESCRIPTION:The weather forecast looks like the 3rd Saturday Road Ride is d
 oubtful. If\, however\, the cycling gods do smile on us\, depart 0900 from 
 office parking lot north of the Starbucks on John Jones Rd.<br>Ride will he
 ad north toward Stallion Station\, returning through Woodland\, with a stop
  for a snack at Pupuseria La Chicana in honor of Raymond ‘Pou-Pou’ Poulidor
 .<br><br>Roughly 41mi\, YOLO-County flat.<br>Similar to the old ‘Tweeners M
 onday Woodland Ride’:<br><a href="https://ridewithgps.com/routes/27694425" 
 target="_blank">https://ridewithgps.com/routes<wbr />/27694425</a><br><br>R
 ide well. Do good things.<br>Robert
LAST-MODIFIED:20250505T005827Z
LOCATION:John Jones\, 2068 John Jones Rd\, Davis\, CA 95616\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:3rd Saturday Long Ride
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
