DTSTAMP:20260327T025937Z
UID:6m9ppq98l72ksskaubrgt22lsj@google.com
CREATED:20250609T220615Z
DESCRIPTION:Sharon Lage and I are leading a summer ride to Ficelle in Winte
 rs for dinner. We will meet on the Russell Bike Path at Lake Boulevard at 5
  pm.\n\nFicelle is a casual tapas restaurant behind Steady Eddy's. There is
  a small indoor dining area and a large outdoor deck. If we are lucky we ca
 n snag a long table.\n\nAccording to Gemini\, sunset on June 12 is at 8:31p
 m and last light is at 9:03 pm. Let's plan to get to Ficelle around 6:00\, 
 eat for one hour and leave at 7:00 pm. If we keep to this schedule\, we wil
 l reach the Russell Bike Path well before sunset. Please have lights on you
 r bike.\n\nSince wind is forecast at 12 mph from the south at 5 pm\, I plan
  to ride my e-bike.\n\nYou can ride any speed you like\, but Sharon and I e
 njoy a touring pace of 10 to 12 miles an hour.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250609T220616Z
LOCATION:Russell Boulevard & Lake Boulevard\, Russell Blvd & Lake Blvd\, Ca
 lifornia 95616\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Ride to Ficelle for Dinner
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
