DESCRIPTION:Marilyn Dewey and Russ Ewers have an alternative ride for you t
 o consider this week.<br><br>On Friday the 15th of November\, we will be le
 ading the inaugural Solano On Friday Tour  …  S - O - F - T  … which will d
 epart at 9:00 AM from the Information Booth just west and south of the Mond
 avi Center round-a-bout …<br><br>The ride will be enjoyed at a relaxed pace
  … for e-bikers and road bikers alike.<br><br>The route will feature beauti
 ful northern Solano County along nearly the same route as the Tuesday slow 
 ride\, with the primary difference only being the Starting Point.  The rout
 e will be approximately 27 miles\, if the Yolano Loop is included\, subject
  to riders preferences.<br><br>The ride will return to the patio adjacent t
 o the South Davis Nugget\, giving the riders an opportunity to choose from 
 libations and snacks from Nugget\, Starbucks or Taqueria Guadalajara.<br><b
 r>This route is a preliminary attempt to offer a different ride along good 
 roads in scenic farm country.  It is likely that this route will be revised
  over time and may even vary from week to week in the future.  Some come al
 ong for the ride.<br><br>The Journey Is The Goal !!!<br><br><a href="https:
 //ridewithgps.com/routes/35726331">Ride by GPS </a>- similar except for the
  start at the <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/4AhcX93dKncC6vpn8">UC Davis 
 Visitors Center on Old Davis Rd</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20241114T155337Z
LOCATION:UC Davis Visitor Information\, Old Davis Rd\, Davis\, CA 95616\, U
 SA
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:SOFT Ride
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
