DESCRIPTION:DBC will resume meetings after a summer hiatus on Monday Septem
 ber 8th at 7pm\, at the Bike Hall of Fame on 2nd and B streets in Davis.   
   This will be an informal Ice Cream social.\n\nIf anyone has any children 
 or grandchildren they are invited to attend.  Weather permitting it would b
 e better for us to enjoy our ice cream outside the BHOF.\n\n\nIf anyone wou
 ld like to help with purchasing ice cream or serving please let me know.\n\
 n\nDavid Joshel\n\nPresident
