 P</b>\; attendance is limited by the venue so RSVP early to get your spot<u
 l><li>Food:  Light appetizers\, ham\, turkey\, stuffed mushrooms\, and dess
 erts from Simply Sastisfied Catering.</li><li>Drinks:  Non-alcoholic bevera
 ges provided.  BYOB (cups/ice provided).</li><li>Presentation of Outstandin
 g Volunteer and Lifetime Achievement Awards</li><li>Voting for 2026 Board O
 fficers</li><li>Please <a href="https://davisbikeclub.wildapricot.org/Email
 Tracker/LinkTracker.ashx?linkAndRecipientCode=rj%2fKOWd3yUbapFrsKQkQA41GWk3
