 eKjNdkWDRf0%3d" target="_blank">use this link to RSVP</a>\, required by Dec
 ember 1st to attend. <strong>Members only.</strong></li><li>Ample bike park
 ing is available on the east side of the venue.</li><li>Registration may be
  closed early if registrations exceed the venue capacity.</li></ul><p><br>L
 ooking forward to seeing you there!</p><p>Michael St Paul\, DBC Vice-Presid
 ent<br><a href="mailto:vice-president@davisbikeclub.org" target="_blank">vi
 ce-president@davisbikeclub.<wbr />org</a><br></p></td></tr></tbody></table>
