DESCRIPTION:Presentation by City of Davis on transportation planning and up
 coming projects. Bapu Vaitla\, City Council member representing District 1 
 (West Davis)\, and Ryan Chapman\, Director of Public Works and Transportati
 on for the City of Davis will discuss current and future transportation pro
 jects in the city. Learn about how the City approaches transportation plann
 ing and works to improve the experience of cyclists in the community.<p>Com
 e join us for a social gathering\, an interesting cycling topic.</p><p><br>
 </p>
