DESCRIPTION:<br><a href="https://ridewithgps.com/routes/51450676" target="_
 blank">https://ridewithgps.com/<wbr />routes/51450676</a><br><br>My plan fo
 r Saturday morning\, starting and finishing at the Westlake Shopping Center
  parking lot\, is to ride the above variation of One Bump over Cantelow Roa
 d. The round trip is 47.8 miles and includes 1\,188 feet of climbing. We wi
 ll depart at 8 am.<br><br>We'll take a slightly different route on the flat
 s to Cantelow Road\, regrouping at the summit. Unless we have a strong tail
 wind\, the pace will be 19 mph or less on the flats for the first hour plus
 . Riders can go as fast as they like up the climbs.<br><br>On the return th
 rough Winters\, we'll take a brief rest at Steady Eddy's. We will then ride
  back to Davis at a conversational pace &lt\;20 mph. <br><br>Back at Westla
 ke Shopping Center\, <b>everyone on the ride is required to enjoy one beer 
 at Super Owl.</b> There are nearby restaurants\, if you want to use that ma
 lted beverage to wash down your lunch.<br><br>The weather tomorrow afternoo
 n will be hot. But it should be decent from 8 am to noon with a breeze unde
 r 5 mph in the Davis area\, perhaps a bit stronger west of here. Remember t
 o bring sufficient water and snacks and at least enough money to buy your r
 equisite craft beer.<br><br>See you mañana.<br><br>Rich Rifkin
LAST-MODIFIED:20250628T031819Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:One Bump ride\, start\, Super Owl finish
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
