DESCRIPTION:Meet in front of the Davis  Vets center on 14th st at 11:00am o
 n Tuesdays.\nWe will decide where to go for lunch based on the input from r
 iders.   \nWoodland\, Winters and Dixon are the usual destinations.   The p
 ace is pretty relaxed\, usually 14-15 mph\, with  occasional regroups. \n\n
 \nThanks\, David Joshel\nPhone 530-400-3288
LAST-MODIFIED:20260303T230350Z
LOCATION:City of Davis: Veterans Memorial Center\, 203 E 14th St\, Davis\, 
 CA 95616\, USA
